the secret of kells is a 2009 french-belgian-irish animated fantasy film animated by cartoon saloon that premiered on 8 february 2009 at the 59th berlin international film festival . it went into wide release in belgium and france on 11 february , and ireland on 3 march . it was directed by tomm moore and nora twomey , produced by paul young , didier brunner and vivian van fleteren , written by fabrice ziolkowski , distributed by gébéka films , kinepolis film distribution , studiocanal and buena vista , edited by fabienne alvarez-giro and music composed by bruno coulais and kíla . it stars evan mcguire , brendan gleeson , christen mooney , mick lally , michael mcgrath , liam hourican , paul tylak and paul young . it was nominated for the academy award for best animated feature .